OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister can't give        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcertainty over pensions    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frate                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Foreign Secretary James Cleverly has   
OL,6, said he cannot give people "certainty" 
OL,7, over how much their pensions will      
OL,8, increase by next year.                 
OL,10,FState pensions were due to rise by     
OL,11,Fabout 10% in April 2023, which would   
OL,12,Ftake the weekly payment from #185.15 to
OL,13,Fjust over #200.                        
OL,15,FBut the funding formula that guaranteed
OL,16,Fthat rise - known as the "triple lock" 
OL,17,F- could be ditched to make savings.    
OL,19,FIt comes as Liz Truss prepares to face 
OL,20,FMPs at Prime Minister's Questions.     
